| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3451 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 41cf33cf-d14f-5a21-944e-000b6d9b1216"
